_____________________________________________
1)
To creat a hiiden folder/file:-

mkdir .folder => creat a new hidden folder.
touch .file.txt => creat a new hidden.
- - - - - - - - - - 

To display the hidden file/folder:-
ls -a => To display all hidden files and folders.

_____________________________________________
2)
To create multiple nested directories:-

mkdir -p ex1/ex2/ex3.txt

______________________________________________
3)
How to append a message to a file without a newline character:-

echo "first line" > file.tex 
echo "first line" >> file.tex 

